2026-02-07 18:49:20 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[IsEmailVerified], [u].[IsActive], [u].[CreatedAt], (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM([a].[Balance]), 0.0)
    FROM [Accounts] AS [a]

2026-02-07 18:51:20 [INF] Executed DbCommand (41ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[IsEmailVerified], [u].[IsActive], [u].[CreatedAt], (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM([a].[Balance]), 0.0)
    FROM [Accounts] AS [a]

2026-02-07 21:19:27 [INF] Executed DbCommand (12ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[IsEmailVerified], [u].[IsActive], [u].[CreatedAt], (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM([a].[Balance]), 0.0)
    FROM [Accounts] AS [a]
